query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(mc cn) NoMergeJoin(ci cn mc an1) NoMergeJoin(an1 ci cn mc t) NoMergeJoin(an1 ci cn mc t rt) NoMergeJoin(an1 ci cn mc rt t n1) */ select min(an1.name) AS costume_designer_pseudo,
min(t.title) AS movie_with_costumes
from movie_companies AS mc
inner join company_name AS cn
on mc.company_id = cn.id AND cn.country_code = '[sm]'
inner join cast_info AS ci
on ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id
inner join aka_name AS an1
on an1.person_id = ci.person_id
inner join title AS t
on ci.movie_id = t.id AND t.id = mc.movie_id
inner join role_type AS rt
on ci.role_id = rt.id AND rt.role = 'producer'
inner join name AS n1
on an1.person_id = n1.id AND n1.id = ci.person_id;
